RPPA TCGA-SARC

Alicia Pliego

1 RPPA TCGA-SARC analysis

1.1 tSNE for RPPA TCGA-SARC colored by HRD34 score

Data was downloaded from GDC Data Commons and was normalize by quantile normalization. Data was divided into two groups (HRDhigh/HRDlow) for comparison. Linear regression was applies using the R package limma (@limma).

1.2 Table of differentially expressed proteins in the HRDhigh group vs the HRDlow.

Table only shows proteins with an adjusted pvalue < 0.05. - Positive logFC indicates overexpressed and - Negative logFC indicated underexpressed.

1.3 Heatmap Differentially expressed proteins HRDhigh vs HRDlow in all cases TCGA-SARC
